name: Lewis Nicholas Deshun
description: It’s hard to describe a complex personality in few words. I’ll try saying the most important things just to make a picture… I’m smart, funny, loving, caring, kissing, affectionate, passionate and more others… I am very sensitive and i am giving myself completely in a relationship. I hate lies so i am very honest. An analytic mind and, at the same time, a very romantic nature. I treat everyone the way i like to be treated myself. I got 1 son living downtown with her grandma and she is my life. I like reading, especially science-fiction, watching on tv, walking hand in hand
